{"tid":871170,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍跌勢起動　嘉湖及栢慧呎價重回1萬元","createTime":"2018-10-21T16:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T00:55:01.000Z","uid":51294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"27187728d99630dc9d65b9ccf30b772a158b9eca","tid":871170,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"10月21日(日) 16:10<br />\n<br />\n天水圍二手私樓屋苑掀跌價潮，市場消息稱，區內栢慧豪園第3座高層A室，實用面積494方呎，開價620萬港元放售，有大型銀行對上址網上估價達625萬元，但屋苑經歷一個多月靜市後，減價至525萬元才售出，呎價10,628元，回歸年初價位。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於另一個同區指標嘉湖山莊，景湖居9座有兩個兩房單位，實用面積均為446方呎，市傳同以約460萬元，呎價約1.03萬元成交，屬同類近期低位。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181021/mobile/bkn-20181021161003002-1021_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181021%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181021161003002-1021_00842_001.html&d=m%2B0%2BLbE%2FOxXva2acS8PPQQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5af003ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181021/mobile/bkn-20181021161003002-1021_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b52cd21f027dc456874abbec1ed4aa9a67423a8a","tid":871170,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"6cfd9d4ecaf163a5134dc35ae7626c422f76a752","tid":871170,"uid":36296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T17:21:31.000Z","msg":"重回5000呎先報啦"},{"pid":"291cb38ef041676324c79e688ca3e69dff888349","tid":871170,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3810329a167b1ae404fc0646a350e001af5b45aa","tid":871170,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T18:07:28.000Z","msg":"跌到4000就買"},{"pid":"e6e6027e286f4bb245a8d2c1998679ab1067a4b6","tid":871170,"uid":137725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"收聲啦唔撚計呀<br />\n<br />\n屌曬你地全部人呀"},{"pid":"5f9bfa1ea71